<div class="p-3 mt-3 border-0 bd-example m-0 border-0 row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4">
  <div class="col"> 
      <div class="card ms-auto h-100" >
        <%=  image_tag "landing_page1.jpg", alt: "image de profile" %>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="me-auto h-100 mt-5" >
    <h1 class="mb-4">(Re)Découvrez vos talents sportifs</h1>
    <h5 class="mb-4">Ici, vous pouvez loué un lieu de sport partout en france</h5>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. 
    Donec dapibus malesuada enim eu dapibus. 
    Donec tempor orci ut orci tempus vulputate. 
    In eleifend nibh quis lacus luctus, vitae mattis lorem cursus. 
    Mauris consequat laoreet est nec consectetur. Integer non tempor nunc. 
    Phasellus imperdiet purus eu turpis venenatis, eget molestie risus finibus. 
    Mauris eu tortor mi. Aliquam imperdiet eros vitae feugiat ullamcorper. 
    Nunc porttitor mollis mauris, ac rhoncus metus finibus molestie.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center vh-100" >
    <h5 class="col-12 text-center" style="max-width: 30rem;">Vous disposez d’équipement sportif de qualité et vous souhaitez les partagés avec la communauté ? </h5>
    <div class="card border-0 d-flex justify-content-center mb-4">
      <%=  image_tag "landing_page2.png", alt: "image de profile" %>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
      <%= link_to "Proposez votre équipement a la communauté", new_workout_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg m-0" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="album py-5 text-center container">
  <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-3 g-3">
    <% @workouts.take(3).each_with_index do |workout, index| %> 
      <a href="<%= workout_path(workout) %>">
        <div class="card shadow" style="max-width: 40rem; height: 350px;">
          <%= image_tag 'logokeella.png', alt: "workout-image", style:"width: 100%; height: 50%; object-fit: cover;"  %>
          <div class="card-title-container border rounded p-2">
            <h5 class="card-title"><%= workout.title %></h5>
            <i class="bi bi-star-fill">Note de l'hote</i>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <li class="list-group-item">
                  <i class="bi bi-currency-dollar"></i>
                  <%= workout.price %>
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                  <i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i>
                  <%= workout.city.name %>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <li class="list-group-item">
                  <i class="bi bi-calendar-x-fill"></i>
                  <%= workout.end_date.strftime("%d/%m/%Y %H:%M") %>
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                  <i class="bi bi-calendar-check"></i>
                  <%= workout.start_date.strftime("%d/%m/%Y %H:%M") %>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
  <%= link_to "Voir toutes les locations", workouts_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg m-0" %>
</div>